@everyone We've been hard at work on our VRF implementation, and tomorrow it is finally time to unveil it. Join us for our first community call where @robert_empiric will walk us through Empiric Network's VRF implementation on testnet. We will be joined by various game developers from the StarkNet ecosystem, and everyone is welcome to join, give us feedback, and ask questions!

The call will take place at 10:30am EST in the "Community Calls" channel. Hope to see you there for this exciting milestone!

